title: Migos On iLoveMakonnen Coming Out As Gay: “That’s Wack, Bro”
text: Rap music might not be as homophobic as it once was, but we've got a long way to go before it's free of homophobia. Case in point: Last month, Atlanta sing-rapper iLoveMakonnen came out as gay on Twitter, and most of the reaction was loving and supportive. But the great Atlanta rap trio Migos, … More »
